                            <article id="post-1072" class="cf article centred post-1072 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-articles tag-brian-eno tag-david-bowie tag-pink-floyd tag-radiohead" role="article" itemscope itemprop="blogPost" itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">

